hy-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-10Z","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23760,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/21\/prophet-prays-thaqif-guided\/","url_meta":{"origin":3905,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet prays for his enemies to be guided","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the arrows of the tribe of Thaqif have pierced us, so pray against them!\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, guide the tribe of Thaqif!\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3942 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6555,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/umar-converts-to-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":3905,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Umar: The Prophet prays for Umar&#8217;s conversion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, strengthen Islam with one of two men whom you love more: Abu Jahl or Umar ibn al-Khattab.\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cThe most beloved of the two was Umar.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3681 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/04\/allah-answers-dua-yunus\/","url_meta":{"origin":3905,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Yunus: Allah answers supplication of Prophet Jonah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplication of Jonah, Dhul Nun, when he called upon Allah inside the belly of the whale was this, 'There is no God but You, glory be to You for I have certainly been among the wrongdoers,'\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37874,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/afiyah-ask-allah-wellness\/","url_meta":{"origin":3905,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Afiyah: Ask Allah for wellness in this life and next","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me something to ask Allah Almighty.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk Allah for wellness.\u201d I waited for some days, then I came back, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, teach me something.\u201d The Prophet said to me,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"c